data.description: Looking for a quaint home 2 miles away from Palmer Woods? Look no further than 19241 St. Aubin Street! This charming 2 story home features durable hardwood oak colored flooring. As soon as you step inside, you'll be greeted by elegant French doors that open up to a spacious living room w cherry wood slacks on the tall 9ft ceilings, perfect for entertaining guests. Nice dining room leading to 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom. Located upstairs are 2 large bedrooms and the primary bath. Primary bath even holds additional storage space. There is a spacious basement waiting for your TLC. With a little bit of finishing touches, this house would be ready for your enjoyment. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity! Call today to schedule a private showing 3137285282
